2	 * Layerinfinite — routes/admin/actions.ts
3	 * Admin action management endpoints.
4	 * ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
5	 * REST endpoints:
6	 * POST /        — register a new action
7	 * GET  /        — list all registered actions
8	 * GET  /:id     — get a single action
9	 * PUT  /:id     — enable/disable an action
10	 *
11	 * Legacy aliases are kept for compatibility:
12	 * POST /register-action, GET /actions, GET /actions/:id, PUT /actions/:id
13	 *
14	 * Authentication via admin-auth.ts middleware (customer_admin).
